    "We then add the curated TD data into the original training data of NExT-QA for training (∼ 4.5K).",
    "The results in Tab.",
    "5 show that this simple data augmentation significantly boosts the model performance on both the temporal description (TD) and temporal exchange (TE) probes, and slightly improves the performance on the original test set (TO) for temporal understanding.",
    "The consistent improvements on all test settings thus demonstrate the effectiveness of such data argumentation towards more robust temporal understanding.",
    "Additionally, we observe profound improvements on TD test probe."
